	* goffice/graph/gog-graph.c (gog_graph_view_handle_event): correct use
	of GDK_POINTER_MOTION_HINT_MASK, according to gtk tutorial. There's
	still a problem with foocanvas which seems to eat a GDK_BUTTON_PRESS
	event.

