	(gog_renderer_pop_clip): ditto. Free clip_path.
	(gog_renderer_get_rectangle_vpath): new.
	* goffice/graph/gog-view.c (gog_view_render): clipping region is a
	path now.
	* plugins/plot_barcol/gog-line.c (gog_line_view_render): ditto.
